<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>A woman in her 30s is in hospital after she was shot outside a shop in Maida Vale, London.</p>

<p>Police have set up a crime scene on Harrow Road after she was gunned down before at 11.50pm yesterday.</p>

<p>The woman was treated at the scene before being taken to hospital. Police await an update on her condition. </p>

<p>Shocking images show the cordon around a blood stained crime scene near the junction at Ashmore Road. </p>

<p>Police have set up a crime scene on Harrow Road, London, after a woman in her 30s was shot at 11.50pm yesterday</p>

<p>MPS Westminster said: 'A woman aged in her 30s was shot at around 11.50pm in Harrow Rd near junction with Ashmore Rd. </p>

<p>'She was treated at the scene before being taken to hospital. We await an update on her condition. A crime scene is in place. No arrest. </p>

<p>'Witnesses pls call 101 ref 8710/11Sep.'</p>

<p>Metropolitan Police have been approached for comment. </p>
